{
  "stem": "5388.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I brought him stamps, and he used to give me butter and bread.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So I already established that I'm poor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And so I said that I am going to Oberfeldwebel [GERMAN], to bring him stamps, to exchange stamps.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I show them the stamps with me, which I had stamps with me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And didn't look like a Jewish boy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Keep in mind, I was a blond fellow with that-- with that cap that I showed you there, that we have.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "This was my cap I was wearing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I remember when I used to sometimes go and stay outside the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Just in case anybody thought maybe it's a Jewish boy, I used to take my finger and put it against the nose like that to make it so up nose that really nobody would think it's a Jewish boy.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And what, a young boy is digging his nose, so he's playing with his nose, and that was all.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But anyway, so they saw I have stamps.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I told them where this Oberfeldwebel [GERMAN] is, that he's in the school.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Master Sergeant, right.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I went in the place to the-- where used to be the-- the Russian school during 1940, '41, OK?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I passed there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I come there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It-- it-- it's quiet suddenly, and an unteroffizier-- which would be a sergeant-- walks out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And what are you doing here?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't-- I don't-- I can tell it in German, but it's basically it goes, what are you doing here, or get out of here.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I say, oh, I came to Oberfeldwebel [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I give him the same spiel over again.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I came to Oberfeldwebel to see him and exchange for the stamps.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
